      "id": "PopularPost218665",
      "post_content": "My favorite trick when playing Numot (or his [*Planar Cousin*](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=124062)) is to call out the 6 \"components\" that make up Devastator. \"**Scrapper!** **Mixmaster!** **Long Haul!** [**Hook!**](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=48420) [**Bonecrusher!**](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=245230) [**Scavenger!**](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=214666) Transform, **PHASE TWO!**\" (Imagine this line in Frank Welker's Megatron voice.)",
      "posted_by": "Cybertronian",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost218665\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">My favorite trick when playing Numot (or his <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=124062\"><i>Planar Cousin</i></a>) is to call out the 6 \"components\" that make up Devastator. \"<b>Scrapper!</b> <b>Mixmaster!</b> <b>Long Haul!</b> <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=48420\"><b>Hook!</b></a> <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=245230\"><b>Bonecrusher!</b></a> <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=214666\"><b>Scavenger!</b></a> Transform, <b>PHASE TWO!</b>\" (Imagine this line in Frank Welker's Megatron voice.)</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy3000\">Cybertronian</span>\r\n                                (1/3/2012 4:15:29 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postRating_starRati